sentences.sentence: We generally believe in pre-set, long-lived and small bullseyes.
sentences.translation: 我们通常相信预先设好的，长期和小的牛眼靶心。

sentences.sentence: Adrenalin junkies can get their fix by balancing sharp hatchets and double-edged axes over their heads before hurling them at painted wooden bullseyes.
sentences.translation: 喜欢这种刺激运动的人会先在头顶平衡一下锋利的短柄小斧和双刃斧，瞄准位置，然后再向彩色的木制靶眼投过去。
